1
00:00:04,104 --> 00:00:06,037
[ Bell Dings ]

2
00:00:06,107 --> 00:00:09,040
AFTER THE CEREMONY,
I'LL HAVE YOU TRANSFERRED
BACK TO THE HOTEL.

3
00:00:09,110 --> 00:00:12,043
I'VE ALSO TAKEN THE LIBERTY
OF CONTACTING
A REAL ESTATE AGENT.

4
00:00:12,113 --> 00:00:14,079
WE NEED TO TALK.
I'M BUSY.

5
00:00:18,218 --> 00:00:19,818
WHO'S THE GUY?

6
00:00:19,886 --> 00:00:22,153
NOT NOW, OKAY?

7
00:00:24,725 --> 00:00:26,725
MY SINCEREST APOLOGIES.

8
00:00:52,286 --> 00:00:54,085
<i>[ Shutter Clicking ]</i>

9
00:01:03,096 --> 00:01:05,730
<i> [ Elevator Bell Dings ]</i>

10
00:01:23,350 --> 00:01:25,750
EXCUSE ME.
<i>[ Shutters Continue</i>
<i>  Clicking ]</i>

11
00:01:35,663 --> 00:01:37,262
<i> [ Gavel Raps ]</i>

12
00:01:37,331 --> 00:01:41,266
<i>WELCOME TO WHAT I'M SURE</i>
<i>IS THE BEGINNING</i>
<i>OF EXCITING NEW LIVES...</i>

13
00:01:41,335 --> 00:01:43,902
AS UNITED STATES CITIZENS.

14
00:01:43,971 --> 00:01:47,338
<i>IF YOU'LL RAISE</i>
<i>YOUR RIGHT HANDS</i>
<i>AND REPEAT AFTER ME--</i>

15
00:01:47,408 --> 00:01:50,108
<i> I HEREBY DECLARE,</i>
<i> ON OATH,</i>

16
00:01:50,177 --> 00:01:52,477
I HEREBY DECLARE,
ON OATH,

17
00:01:52,546 --> 00:01:57,849
<i>THAT I ABSOLUTELY AND ENTIRELY</i>
<i>RENOUNCE AND ABJURE...</i>
[ Thinking: Screeching ]

18
00:01:57,918 --> 00:02:00,685
THAT I ABSOLUTELY
AND ENTIRELY
RENOUNCE AND ABJURE...

19
00:02:00,754 --> 00:02:06,358
<i>ALL ALLEGIANCE AND FIDELITY</i>
<i>TO ANY FOREIGN PRINCE...</i>

20
00:02:06,426 --> 00:02:10,161
ALL ALLEGIANCE AND FIDELITY
TO ANY FOREIGN PRINCE,

21
00:02:10,230 --> 00:02:13,097
<i>[ Judge ] POTENTATE,</i>
<i>STATE OR SOVEREIGNTY...</i>
[ Shouting In Cambodian ]

22
00:02:13,166 --> 00:02:16,000
<i>[ Candidates ] POTENTATE,</i>
<i>STATE OR SOVEREIGNTY--</i>

23
00:02:16,069 --> 00:02:19,337
<i> [ Shouting Continues</i>
<i> In Cambodian ]</i>

24
00:02:19,406 --> 00:02:22,006
<i>[ Gavel Rapping ]</i>
<i>[ Judge ]</i>
<i>MA'AM, PLEASE!</i>

25
00:02:22,075 --> 00:02:24,476
<i>MA'AM!</i>
<i>[ Gavel Rapping Continues ]</i>

26
00:02:24,545 --> 00:02:26,477
<i>[ Judge ]</i>
<i>SECURITY!</i>
[ Cambodian ]

27
00:02:26,546 --> 00:02:29,280
<i>SOMEONE PLEASE</i>
<i>GET SECURITY HERE NOW!</i>
<i>[ Gavel Rapping Continues ]</i>

28
00:02:29,349 --> 00:02:31,116
<i>ORDER! PLEASE!</i>

29
00:02:31,184 --> 00:02:33,986
<i> - [ Fire Alarm Ringing ]</i>
<i> - [ Judge ]</i>
<i> PLEASE REMAIN CALM!</i>

30
00:02:34,054 --> 00:02:38,523
<i>REMAIN CALM</i>
<i>AND FILE IN AN ORDERLY MANNER</i>
<i>TO THE NEAREST EXIT!</i>

31
00:02:38,592 --> 00:02:40,558
<i>PLEASE REMAIN CALM!</i>

32
00:02:43,230 --> 00:02:45,797
[ Shouting In Cambodian ]

33
00:02:48,301 --> 00:02:51,403
<i>[ Fire Alarm</i>
<i>  Continues Ringing ]</i>

34
00:03:07,254 --> 00:03:09,053
[ Muttering In Cambodian ]

35
00:03:24,771 --> 00:03:27,606
DID YOU SEE THE LOOK
ON THAT POOR WOMAN'S FACE?

36
00:03:27,674 --> 00:03:32,844
I KNOW SHE'S BLIND,
BUT SHE ACTED LIKE
SHE'D SEEN THE DEVIL HIMSELF.

37
00:03:40,353 --> 00:03:43,488
<i>[ Man Narrating ]</i>
<i>THERE ARE PRETENDERS AMONG US.</i>

38
00:03:43,557 --> 00:03:45,490
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>I WAS TAKEN FROM MY FAMILY.</i>

39
00:03:45,559 --> 00:03:49,127
<i>THIRTY-SIX HOURS AND HE'S</i>
<i>ALREADY DEMONSTRATING MORE</i>
<i>TALENT THAN ANY OF OUR OTHERS.</i>

40
00:03:49,196 --> 00:03:52,597
<i>HOW MANY PEOPLE DIED</i>
<i>BECAUSE OF WHAT I THOUGHT UP?</i>

41
00:03:52,666 --> 00:03:56,101
SINCE I BROKE OUT,
I'VE SPENT EVERY MOMENT
SEARCHING FOR MY PAST.

42
00:03:56,170 --> 00:03:58,370
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>HE'S A PRETENDER--</i>

43
00:03:58,439 --> 00:04:01,206
<i>A GENIUS WHO CAN BECOME</i>
<i>ANYONE THAT HE WANTS TO BE.</i>

44
00:04:01,275 --> 00:04:04,008
-<i> THE CENTRE WANTS HIM ALIVE.</i>
- PREFERABLY.

45
00:04:04,077 --> 00:04:07,011
<i>- [ Miss Parker ] HE DEFENDS</i>
<i>  THE WEAK AND ABUSED.</i>
<i>- [ Jarod ] LIFE'S A GIFT.</i>

46
00:04:18,791 --> 00:04:21,259
-<i> YOU A DOCTOR?</i>
- I AM TODAY.

47
00:04:28,334 --> 00:04:31,870
<i>[ Broots ]</i>
<i>I PULLED A STILL FRAME OFF</i>
<i>THE FRONT GATE SECURITY CAMERA.</i>

48
00:04:31,939 --> 00:04:36,174
WELL, HE SIGNED IN
UNDER THE NAME KI MAK.
SOUNDS THAI.

49
00:04:36,243 --> 00:04:40,045
CAMBODIAN. RUN IT THROUGH
OUR INTERPOL SERVER,
SEE WHAT POPS UP.

50
00:04:40,113 --> 00:04:41,713
- OKAY.
- HE HAS A TATTOO.

51
00:04:41,782 --> 00:04:43,782
- A TATTOO?
- ON THE BACK OF HIS RIGHT HAND.

52
00:04:43,851 --> 00:04:45,784
IT'S A SNAKE EATING ITSELF.

53
00:04:45,852 --> 00:04:47,518
I'LL MAKE A NOTE.

54
00:04:49,522 --> 00:04:52,490
-THINK LYLE IS UP TO SOMETHING?
-I KNOW LYLE IS UP TO SOMETHING.

55
00:04:52,559 --> 00:04:54,960
THE QUESTION IS, WHAT?

56
00:04:55,029 --> 00:04:59,597
<i> [ Woman ]</i>
<i> JUST MAKE SURE THE INVOICES</i>
<i> ARE SIGNED AND INITIALED.</i>

57
00:04:59,666 --> 00:05:01,599
THANKS.
<i> [ Phone Ringing ]</i>

58
00:05:03,236 --> 00:05:05,237
<i>[ Woman ]</i>
<i>AGENT BERGER, I.N.S.</i>

59
00:05:06,473 --> 00:05:08,406
<i>UH, NO, SIR,</i>

60
00:05:08,475 --> 00:05:12,376
I CAN'T DEPORT SOMEONE
BECAUSE YOU DON'T LIKE
THE PRICE OF CIGARETTES.

61
00:05:12,445 --> 00:05:15,713
WELL, I SUGGEST
YOU SHOP AT ANOTHER STORE.

62
00:05:15,782 --> 00:05:18,483
NO, SIR, THAT'S--
THAT'S NOT A JOKE.
THAT'S AMERICA.

63
00:05:18,552 --> 00:05:20,485
[ Line Hangs Up,
Dial Tone ]

64
00:05:20,554 --> 00:05:22,386
CAN I HELP YOU,
MR., UH--

65
00:05:22,455 --> 00:05:24,589
AGENT. ELLIS.
JAROD ELLIS.

66
00:05:24,658 --> 00:05:26,991
I WAS SENT DOWN
ABOUT A BLIND WOMAN.

67
00:05:27,060 --> 00:05:29,861
SENT DOWN?
YES, FROM D.C.

68
00:05:29,930 --> 00:05:33,699
I WAS WORKING A CASE OUTSIDE
OF STOCKBRIDGE WHEN WE GOT
THE CALL FROM YOUR OFFICE.

69
00:05:33,767 --> 00:05:36,067
FROM WHAT AGENT?

70
00:05:36,136 --> 00:05:38,603
<i> RINKER.</i>

71
00:05:38,672 --> 00:05:40,739
- MIKE RINKER?
-<i> [ Phone Ringing ]</i>

72
00:05:43,343 --> 00:05:45,743
- JACK.
-<i> [ Ringing Continues ]</i>

73
00:05:48,915 --> 00:05:50,915
EXCUSE ME.

74
00:05:51,951 --> 00:05:53,885
<i>[ Punching Keypad ]</i>

75
00:05:53,954 --> 00:05:56,287
<i> [ Man On Radio ]</i>
<i> SECURITY</i>
<i> TO THE SOUTHWEST DOOR.</i>

76
00:05:56,356 --> 00:05:59,424
<i>CAROL. IS JACK RINKER</i>
<i>STILL IN HIS OFFICE?</i>

77
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:06,465
HE'S GONE.

78
00:06:06,533 --> 00:06:09,701
WOULD YOU GET ME
HIS CAR PHONE? THANKS.

79
00:06:09,770 --> 00:06:11,803
I GIVE UP.

80
00:06:11,871 --> 00:06:15,307
ONE HOUR, AND ALL I GET IS
HER NAME AND THE SAME THING
OVER AND OVER AGAIN.

81
00:06:15,375 --> 00:06:17,908
[ Repeats Phrase Twice
In Cambodian ]

82
00:06:17,977 --> 00:06:21,946
<i>I'M FLUENT IN FIVE ASIAN</i>
<i>LANGUAGES, BUT I'LL BE DAMNED IF</i>
<i>I KNOW WHAT SHE'S TRYIN' TO SAY.</i>

83
00:06:22,015 --> 00:06:26,051
SHE'S THIRSTY.
SHE WOULD LIKE
A DRINK OF WATER.

84
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:28,486
- YOU SPEAK CAMBODIAN?
- DOESN'T EVERYBODY?

85
00:06:28,554 --> 00:06:32,757
I'VE GOT JACK RINKER
ON A CAR PHONE.
SHOULD I PUT HIM THROUGH?

86
00:06:40,867 --> 00:06:43,802
TELL HIM
TO HAVE A GOOD VACATION.

87
00:06:43,870 --> 00:06:45,670
SHE'S ALL YOURS.

88
00:07:20,407 --> 00:07:25,277
KIM CHAY.
[ Speaking Cambodian ]
JAROD.

89
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:29,513
[ Speaking Cambodian ]

90
00:07:37,356 --> 00:07:39,323
COULD WE TRY THIS IN ENGLISH?

91
00:07:41,895 --> 00:07:45,063
COULD YOU TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED
TODAY AT THE CEREMONY?

92
00:07:52,038 --> 00:07:54,539
I MEAN YOU NO HARM.

93
00:08:01,181 --> 00:08:04,749
<i>WELL, YOU'RE MY SECOND</i>
<i>SURPRISE VISIT FROM D.C. TODAY.</i>

94
00:08:04,817 --> 00:08:06,985
- SECOND?
- AGENT JAROD ELLIS?

95
00:08:07,053 --> 00:08:08,753
JAROD?

96
00:08:08,821 --> 00:08:11,956
6'2", 180 POUNDS,
DARK HAIR, DARK EYES?

97
00:08:12,025 --> 00:08:14,358
- YOU KNOW HIM?
- WE'VE MET.

98
00:08:14,427 --> 00:08:17,094
MAY I SEE YOUR IDENTIFICATION?

99
00:08:18,932 --> 00:08:22,167
I'M AGENT GREENE.
THIS IS AGENT HILL.
INTERNAL DIVISION.

100
00:08:22,235 --> 00:08:24,836
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>I REALIZE THIS</i>
<i>IS ALL VERY CONFUSING,</i>

101
00:08:24,904 --> 00:08:28,440
BUT I CAN'T HELP YOU
UNLESS I KNOW WHAT'S GOING ON.

102
00:08:29,442 --> 00:08:31,375
IT WAS REPORTED...

103
00:08:31,445 --> 00:08:35,847
THAT YOU KEPT SAYING
THE WORD "BUTCHER" OVER AND OVER
AGAIN AT THE CEREMONY.

104
00:08:35,916 --> 00:08:37,982
<i>CAN YOU TELL ME WHY?</i>

105
00:08:43,457 --> 00:08:45,056
<i> [ Greene ]</i>
<i> WHERE IS HE?</i>

106
00:08:45,125 --> 00:08:49,127
HE'S IN
THE LAST INTERROGATION ROOM,
RIGHT DOWN THE HALL.

107
00:08:58,104 --> 00:09:00,071
<i> DAMN!</i>

108
00:09:00,139 --> 00:09:03,307
<i>[ Ki Mak ]</i>
<i>THIS PROBLEM MUST BE</i>
<i>DEALT WITH IMMEDIATELY.</i>

109
00:09:03,377 --> 00:09:05,643
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

110
00:09:05,712 --> 00:09:08,646
THE WOMAN YOU SAW
AT THE CEREMONY
THIS MORNING...

111
00:09:08,715 --> 00:09:11,249
IS AN UNFORTUNATE LINK
TO MY PAST,

112
00:09:11,317 --> 00:09:14,552
WHICH NOW MAKES HER
A LINK TO YOURS.

113
00:09:14,621 --> 00:09:18,656
I AM SENSITIVE TO YOUR CONCERNS.
BUT IF I'M NOT MISTAKEN,
SHE WAS ALSO BLIND.

114
00:09:20,727 --> 00:09:25,162
UNDER ESTIMATING THE MEEK
HAS BROUGHT MORE THAN ONE ARMY
TO ITS KNEES.

115
00:09:26,700 --> 00:09:28,566
WE HAVE A VERY GOOD ARMY HERE.

116
00:09:30,303 --> 00:09:33,437
<i> - [ Door Opens ]</i>
- [ Clears Throat ]

117
00:09:37,544 --> 00:09:39,544
<i>[ Door Closes ]</i>

118
00:09:41,748 --> 00:09:43,748
DID YOU FIND HER?

119
00:09:43,817 --> 00:09:45,883
[ Whispers ]
THE BLIND WOMAN
HAS BEEN TAKEN.

120
00:09:45,952 --> 00:09:47,652
TAKEN?

121
00:09:48,755 --> 00:09:51,822
BY WHOM?
BY JAROD.

122
00:09:54,661 --> 00:09:57,495
I SUGGEST
YOU TELL YOUR SOLDIERS
THIS IS WAR.

123
00:10:01,034 --> 00:10:04,936
<i>[ Bells Pealing ]</i>
HERE.
LET ME GET THAT.

124
00:10:05,005 --> 00:10:07,972
<i>[ Pealing Continues ]</i>

125
00:10:21,254 --> 00:10:23,821
IS THAT A PICTURE
OF YOUR FAMILY?

126
00:10:23,890 --> 00:10:25,890
MOTHER.

127
00:10:27,727 --> 00:10:30,294
FATHER.
BROTHER.

128
00:10:30,363 --> 00:10:32,129
WHERE ARE THEY NOW?

129
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:34,966
DEAD.

130
00:10:40,907 --> 00:10:43,574
ALL MURDERED BY THE BUTCHER.

131
00:10:45,946 --> 00:10:48,879
ALL MURDERED
BY THE BUTCHER.

132
00:11:05,665 --> 00:11:08,600
<i>[ Broots ]</i>
<i>MAK CAME TO THE UNITED STATES</i>
<i>THREE MONTHS AGO FROM VENEZUELA.</i>

133
00:11:08,668 --> 00:11:10,768
I'M MORE INTERESTED
IN HIS CONNECTION TO LYLE.

134
00:11:10,837 --> 00:11:12,670
WELL, I DON'T KNOW
IF IT'S RELATED,

135
00:11:12,739 --> 00:11:15,873
BUT LYLE'S MADE THREE
BUSINESS TRIPS TO CARACAS
IN THE PAST 12 MONTHS.

136
00:11:15,942 --> 00:11:20,178
<i>AS FAR AS I CAN TELL,</i>
<i>THE CENTRE HAS NO TIES TO ANYONE</i>
<i>OR ANYTHING IN THAT COUNTRY.</i>

137
00:11:20,246 --> 00:11:23,281
- NOT ON PAPER, YOU MEAN.
- I DID HEAR SOMETHING ELSE.

138
00:11:23,350 --> 00:11:25,649
I WAS IN THE BATHROOM
AND I OVERHEARD
A COUPLE SWEEPERS SAYING...

139
00:11:25,718 --> 00:11:29,154
<i> THAT WILLIE</i>
<i> HAD A CLOSE ENCOUNTER</i>
<i> WITH JAROD TODAY.</i>

140
00:11:29,222 --> 00:11:31,056
- WHERE?
- THE MEN'S ROOM, SL-10.

141
00:11:31,124 --> 00:11:33,324
THE ENCOUNTER WITH JAROD,
YOU BOOB.

142
00:11:33,393 --> 00:11:36,227
<i> OH. VIRGINIA.</i>
<i> ACROSS THE RIVER.</i>

143
00:11:36,296 --> 00:11:40,998
BUT THAT'S NOT ALL.
WILLIE HAS BEEN ASSIGNED SPECIAL
TEMPORARY DUTY TO LYLE'S TEAM.

144
00:11:44,604 --> 00:11:47,305
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

145
00:11:48,541 --> 00:11:51,041
TO HAVE A LITTLE TALK
WITH BABY BROTHER.

146
00:12:16,636 --> 00:12:20,204
<i>[ Bells Pealing ]</i>

147
00:12:32,752 --> 00:12:35,119
<i>[ Kim Chay ]</i>
<i>ALL MURDERED BY THE BUTCHER.</i>

148
00:13:11,390 --> 00:13:13,825
IN A HURRY?
EXTREME.

149
00:13:13,893 --> 00:13:16,828
HEY, DID YOU EVER
WONDER WHY
A CAMBODIAN CITIZEN...

150
00:13:16,896 --> 00:13:18,830
WOULD CHOOSE TO
LIVE IN VENEZUELA?

151
00:13:18,898 --> 00:13:21,833
ISN'T THAT INTERESTING?
I SUPPOSE IT COULD BE
THE CLIMATE. OR THE COFFEE.

152
00:13:21,901 --> 00:13:23,835
OR IS IT, PERHAPS,

153
00:13:23,903 --> 00:13:26,838
VENEZUELA
HAS NO EXTRADITION TREATY
WITH THE WEST?

154
00:13:26,906 --> 00:13:29,073
SOMETHING ON YOUR MIND,
SIS?

155
00:13:32,545 --> 00:13:34,478
WHO'S KI MAK?

156
00:13:34,547 --> 00:13:37,715
AND WHY IS RAINES'S GUARD DOG
BABYSITTING HIM?

157
00:13:39,052 --> 00:13:42,053
SHOULDN'T YOU BE
OUT HUNTING FOR JAROD?

158
00:13:48,261 --> 00:13:50,194
IT'S FUNNY
YOU SHOULD ASK THAT,

159
00:13:50,263 --> 00:13:53,865
CONSIDERING I HEARD YOUR PEOPLE
HAD A CLOSE ENCOUNTER
WITH HIM TODAY.

160
00:13:53,933 --> 00:13:55,867
CAN I GET
A LITTLE PRIVACY?

161
00:13:55,935 --> 00:13:58,469
NO.

162
00:13:58,538 --> 00:14:02,774
NOW, DO YOU WANT TO TALK TO ME,
OR SHOULD I GO PUT MY FOOT DOWN
ON WILLIE'S THROAT?

163
00:14:04,610 --> 00:14:07,545
MAK IS A FORMER LEADER
OF THE CAMBODIAN
FREEDOM FIGHTERS.

164
00:14:07,614 --> 00:14:09,647
<i> HE FLED SOUTHEAST ASIA</i>
<i> AFTER SAIGON FELL.</i>

165
00:14:09,715 --> 00:14:11,816
HE WENT UNDERGROUND
FOR HIS OWN SAFETY.

166
00:14:11,884 --> 00:14:14,818
WHAT'S HE DOING HERE?
WE MET IN THAILAND
ABOUT FIVE YEARS AGO.

167
00:14:14,888 --> 00:14:17,821
HE HELPED ME
OUT OF A SITUATION.

168
00:14:17,890 --> 00:14:20,491
<i> I PROMISED</i>
<i> TO RETURN THE FAVOR.</i>

169
00:14:20,560 --> 00:14:22,993
TRUST ME,
OUR LITTLE BRUSH WITH JAROD
WAS PURELY COINCIDENCE.

170
00:14:23,062 --> 00:14:25,063
GO ON.

171
00:14:26,332 --> 00:14:29,267
MAK NEEDED A SPONSOR
TO BECOME A U.S. CITIZEN.

172
00:14:29,335 --> 00:14:32,770
I PULLED SOME STRINGS, GOT HIM
A COMMISSION AS CULTURAL LIAISON
AT THE LOCAL PORT AUTHORITY.

173
00:14:32,839 --> 00:14:34,772
<i> [ Water Running ]</i>

174
00:14:34,841 --> 00:14:37,675
NOW, I SUGGEST
YOU REFOCUS YOUR ATTENTION
ON JAROD...

175
00:14:37,743 --> 00:14:41,345
AND CLIMB OFF MY BACK
BEFORE I RUN OUT
OF PATIENCE.

176
00:14:41,414 --> 00:14:43,915
IS THAT A THREAT?

177
00:14:46,086 --> 00:14:48,086
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

178
00:15:03,937 --> 00:15:06,003
YOU MUST REALLY LIKE
SUGAR DATES.

179
00:15:06,072 --> 00:15:09,273
ACTUALLY...
THEY'RE FOR A FRIEND.

180
00:15:10,343 --> 00:15:12,109
THESE PRAYER BEADS
BELONG TO--

181
00:15:13,179 --> 00:15:14,879
WHO ARE YOU?

182
00:15:14,948 --> 00:15:16,948
I'M A FRIEND OF KIM CHAY'S.

183
00:15:17,016 --> 00:15:19,583
<i>I NEED TO ASK YOU</i>
<i>SOME QUESTIONS.</i>

184
00:15:38,605 --> 00:15:41,538
I BUILT THIS
FOR THE OTHER CAMBODIANS
IN THE AREA.

185
00:15:41,608 --> 00:15:44,875
A LITTLE PIECE
OF WHAT WE LEFT BEHIND.

186
00:15:44,944 --> 00:15:47,444
COME. WE'LL TALK
IN THE BACK ROOM.

187
00:15:52,284 --> 00:15:54,284
PLEASE.

188
00:15:58,958 --> 00:16:02,827
MY COUNTRY IS VERY BEAUTIFUL,
BUT IT HAS SEEN MUCH PAIN--

189
00:16:02,896 --> 00:16:06,797
<i>THE WAR WITH AMERICA,</i>
<i> THE GENOCIDAL MARCH OF POL POT.</i>

190
00:16:07,800 --> 00:16:09,733
THE LEADER
OF THE KHMER ROUGE.

191
00:16:09,803 --> 00:16:11,735
YES.

192
00:16:11,805 --> 00:16:13,805
PLEASE, SIT.

193
00:16:30,823 --> 00:16:33,457
<i>NEARLY 25 YEARS HAS PASSED,</i>

194
00:16:33,526 --> 00:16:36,026
<i>BUT I CAN STILL SMELL</i>
<i>THE BURNING BODIES.</i>

195
00:16:36,095 --> 00:16:41,132
<i>I KEEP THESE TO REMEMBER,</i>
<i>TO NEVER FORGET</i>
<i>WHAT MAN IS CAPABLE OF.</i>

196
00:16:43,903 --> 00:16:47,938
KIM CHAY WAS TORTURED
BY THE KHMER ROUGE.

197
00:16:48,007 --> 00:16:49,840
WORSE, I'M AFRAID.

198
00:16:53,713 --> 00:16:56,647
I HAD A BROTHER
WHO LIVED IN HER VILLAGE.

199
00:16:56,716 --> 00:17:00,418
KIM CHAY'S FAMILY WAS AT HOME
WHEN THE SOLDIERS CAME.

200
00:17:00,486 --> 00:17:03,421
HER FATHER, HER MOTHER,
HER BROTHER...

201
00:17:04,624 --> 00:17:06,557
WERE EXECUTED
IN FRONT OF HER.

202
00:17:06,625 --> 00:17:09,893
<i>YOU SEE,</i>
<i>SHE WASN'T BORN BLIND.</i>

203
00:17:09,962 --> 00:17:13,297
<i>IT IS TOLD THAT SHE ATTACKED</i>
<i>THE OFFICER IN CHARGE...</i>

204
00:17:13,365 --> 00:17:16,300
TO TRY
AND SAVE HER FAMILY,

205
00:17:16,368 --> 00:17:19,136
THAT SHE
DREW HIS BLOOD...

206
00:17:19,205 --> 00:17:21,138
WITH HER BARE HANDS.

207
00:17:21,206 --> 00:17:23,240
<i>SHE WAS SIX YEARS OLD.</i>

208
00:17:26,879 --> 00:17:29,346
THIS MAN?

209
00:17:33,119 --> 00:17:36,854
YES. THIS MAN
IS COLONEL CHEN THON.

210
00:17:36,923 --> 00:17:42,026
HE WAS AN OFFICER
IN THE KHMER ROUGE--
AN EVIL KILLING MONSTER.

211
00:17:42,095 --> 00:17:44,895
<i> DID YOU WITNESS THON</i>
<i> COMMIT THESE MURDERS?</i>

212
00:17:44,964 --> 00:17:46,897
NO.

213
00:17:46,966 --> 00:17:49,733
THE ONLY WITNESS
STILL ALIVE IS KIM CHAY.

214
00:17:49,802 --> 00:17:52,770
<i>SOME OF THE WORST OFFICERS FLED</i>
<i>TO THE GOLDEN TRIANGLE...</i>

215
00:17:52,838 --> 00:17:55,772
<i>AND FLOURISHED</i>
<i>IN THE HEROIN TRADE.</i>

216
00:17:55,841 --> 00:17:58,608
IF COLONEL THON IS HERE,

217
00:17:58,677 --> 00:18:02,412
THEN KIM CHAY'S LIFE
IS IN GREAT DANGER.

218
00:18:02,481 --> 00:18:05,949
<i>AND NOW, I FEAR, SO IS YOURS.</i>

219
00:18:14,227 --> 00:18:17,928
<i>IT TURNS OUT MAK IS BEING</i>
<i>SWORN IN BY THE PORT AUTHORITY</i>
<i>TOMORROW AFTERNOON.</i>

220
00:18:17,997 --> 00:18:21,431
- AND YOU INTEND TO BE THERE?
- LYLE KNOWS HIS TICKET
TO THE TOP IS STILL JAROD.

221
00:18:21,500 --> 00:18:25,936
BUT ALL HE SEEMS TO CARE ABOUT
IS MAKING GOOD ON A PROMISE
HE MADE FIVE YEARS AGO...

222
00:18:26,005 --> 00:18:27,938
TO A VIRTUAL STRANGER.

223
00:18:28,007 --> 00:18:30,173
YOUR POINT?
THERE'S MORE TO THIS
THAN WE KNOW.

224
00:18:30,242 --> 00:18:32,643
AND THIS MAK CHARACTER
IS THE KEY.

225
00:18:32,712 --> 00:18:37,147
HELL, MAYBE JAROD'LL
EVEN MAKE A SURPRISE APPEARANCE.

226
00:18:38,551 --> 00:18:40,484
[ Sighs ]
WELL?

227
00:18:40,553 --> 00:18:43,487
IT'S LIKE MAK
JUST APPEARED
OUT OF THIN AIR.

228
00:18:43,556 --> 00:18:45,289
THERE'S NO
BIRTH CERTIFICATE,

229
00:18:45,358 --> 00:18:46,957
UH, SCHOOL RECORDS,
NOTHING.

230
00:18:47,026 --> 00:18:49,693
- RECORDS CAN DISAPPEAR.
- THEY CAN ALSO BE ERASED.

231
00:18:49,761 --> 00:18:53,664
I TRIED TO OPEN UP
A COMPUTER FILE ON MAK
I HAD FOUND EARLIER TODAY...

232
00:18:53,732 --> 00:18:55,666
TO DOUBLE-CHECK
SOME INFORMATION.

233
00:18:55,735 --> 00:18:58,969
IT WAS GONE. WIPED OUT.
IT'S LIKE ANY HISTORY
OF THIS MAN IS--

234
00:18:59,038 --> 00:19:01,539
- BEING DESTROYED
BEFORE OUR EYES.
- LYLE.

235
00:19:01,607 --> 00:19:04,040
HE TOLD ME
HE MET MAK IN THAILAND.

236
00:19:04,109 --> 00:19:07,044
<i>BROOTS, TAKE THAT PHOTO,</i>
<i>RUN IT AGAIN FOR A VISUAL MATCH.</i>

237
00:19:07,113 --> 00:19:10,180
AND THIS TIME
ISOLATE THE PRIMARY SEARCH
TO SOUTHEAST ASIAN TARGETS--

238
00:19:10,249 --> 00:19:12,215
<i>BOOKS,</i>
<i>MAGAZINES, NEWSPAPERS.</i>

239
00:19:12,284 --> 00:19:15,519
AND HURRY.
THIS GUY COULD BE GONE BEFORE
WE FIND OUT WHO HE REALLY IS.

240
00:19:18,424 --> 00:19:20,424
KIM CHAY?

241
00:19:27,032 --> 00:19:29,666
<i> [ Bells Pealing ]</i>

242
00:19:38,277 --> 00:19:42,979
<i>[ Bell Tolls ]</i>

243
00:19:52,558 --> 00:19:54,558
KIM CHAY?

244
00:20:15,014 --> 00:20:18,448
I KNOW YOU DON'T WANT TO
TALK ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED,

245
00:20:18,517 --> 00:20:21,218
BUT I'M NOT
GOING TO JUST GO AWAY.

246
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:29,793
<i>I NEVER HAD A REAL HOME.</i>

247
00:20:31,464 --> 00:20:33,397
I UNDERSTAND PAIN...

248
00:20:33,466 --> 00:20:35,465
AND LOSS.

249
00:20:39,471 --> 00:20:41,471
TELL ME
ABOUT YOUR BLINDNESS.

250
00:20:47,814 --> 00:20:50,514
IT WAS THE TIME OF YEAR ZERO.

251
00:20:51,784 --> 00:20:56,720
POL POT AND HIS FOLLOWERS
WANTED TO STOP THON,

252
00:20:56,789 --> 00:21:00,624
BEGIN THE WAR WITH THEMSELF
AS THE ONLY POWER.

253
00:21:00,693 --> 00:21:04,127
<i> THE KILLINGS BEGAN</i>
<i> WITH THE TEACHERS.</i>

254
00:21:06,798 --> 00:21:08,732
THEN THE SPIRITUAL LEADERS.

255
00:21:08,800 --> 00:21:11,001
AND FINALLY THE ARTISTS.

256
00:21:12,538 --> 00:21:15,005
YOUR MOTHER AND YOUR FATHER.

257
00:21:17,409 --> 00:21:20,343
THEY WERE WRITER OF POETRY.

258
00:21:20,412 --> 00:21:23,914
WORDS OF COMFORT AND JOY
TO THE PEOPLE.

259
00:21:25,484 --> 00:21:30,253
COLONEL THON MAKE MY FATHER
READ FROM HIS OWN BOOK.

260
00:21:30,322 --> 00:21:32,255
THEN HE KILL HIM...

261
00:21:32,324 --> 00:21:35,625
<i> AND THE OTHER MEMBERS</i>
<i> OF MY FAMILY.</i>

262
00:21:37,196 --> 00:21:40,898
THIS WAS THE DAY
THE SUN WENT AWAY.

263
00:21:44,770 --> 00:21:47,938
I WANT TO HELP THE SUN
RETURN FOR YOU.

264
00:21:49,175 --> 00:21:51,508
BUT I HAVE TO
EXAMINE YOUR EYES.

265
00:21:51,577 --> 00:21:53,877
CAN I DO THAT?

266
00:22:01,086 --> 00:22:05,589
I FEEL YOUR PAIN
AND LONELINESS.

267
00:22:06,792 --> 00:22:10,661
YOU HAVE LOST MANY PEOPLE
THAT YOU LOVE.

268
00:22:16,501 --> 00:22:18,502
YES.

269
00:22:33,619 --> 00:22:37,554
<i>[ Bells Pealing ]</i>

270
00:22:43,662 --> 00:22:45,762
<i> [ Phone Beeps ]</i>

271
00:22:45,831 --> 00:22:47,764
[ Line Rings ]
THIS IS SYDNEY.

272
00:22:47,833 --> 00:22:50,500
I CHECKED KIM CHAY'S EYES.

273
00:22:50,569 --> 00:22:53,737
THERE'S NO SIGN
OF DAMAGE OR DISEASE.

274
00:22:53,806 --> 00:22:56,540
HAVE YOU EVER ENCOUNTERED
SOMETHING CALLED TERROR SILENCE?

275
00:22:56,608 --> 00:22:58,542
FIRST CASES SURFACED...

276
00:22:58,611 --> 00:23:01,511
AFTER THE BOMBING
OF HIROSHIMA AND NAGASAKI.

277
00:23:01,580 --> 00:23:05,449
HOSPITALS BEGAN SEEING
PATIENTS QUITE UNABLE
TO COMMUNICATE.

278
00:23:05,517 --> 00:23:09,052
AND YET THESE PEOPLE
SHOWED NO SIGNS
OF PHYSIOLOGICAL DAMAGE.

279
00:23:09,121 --> 00:23:11,154
THEIR AFFLICTIONS
WERE PSYCHOSOMATIC REACTIONS...

280
00:23:11,223 --> 00:23:13,390
TO THE HORRIFIC SAVAGERY
THEY WITNESSED.

281
00:23:14,960 --> 00:23:19,129
<i>I BELIEVE</i>
<i>THAT KIM CHAY'S BLINDNESS</i>
<i>IS A FORM OF TERROR SILENCE.</i>

282
00:23:19,197 --> 00:23:23,800
WELL, THE HUMAN MIND
IS CAPABLE OF ALMOST ANYTHING
IN ORDER TO PROTECT ITS HOST.

283
00:23:23,869 --> 00:23:27,103
SHE DOESN'T DESERVE
A LIFE OF DARKNESS, SYDNEY.

284
00:23:27,172 --> 00:23:29,105
WHAT APPROACH SHOULD I TAKE?

285
00:23:29,174 --> 00:23:32,108
IN SOME CASES,
THE STRICKEN
HAVE RESPONDED...

286
00:23:32,178 --> 00:23:34,545
BY CONFRONTING
THE OBJECT OF THEIR TERROR.

287
00:23:34,613 --> 00:23:36,547
BUT BE VERY CAREFUL.

288
00:23:36,615 --> 00:23:40,484
IF SHE'S PUSHED TOO HARD,
SHE MAY NEVER EMERGE
FROM THE DARKNESS.

289
00:23:40,552 --> 00:23:42,886
[ Knocking ]
SYDNEY!

290
00:23:44,890 --> 00:23:46,823
OH, BY THE WAY,

291
00:23:46,892 --> 00:23:50,393
MISS PARKER IS PLANNING
A LITTLE TRIP ACROSS
THE RIVER THIS AFTERNOON.

292
00:23:50,463 --> 00:23:53,897
IT SEEMS
SHE HAS BECOME INTERESTED
IN LOCAL POLITICS.

293
00:23:53,966 --> 00:23:57,600
A CERTAIN PORT AUTHORITY
COMMISSION HEARING,
TO BE MORE PRECISE.

294
00:23:57,669 --> 00:23:59,869
I THOUGHT YOU'D BE
INTERESTED TO KNOW.

295
00:23:59,938 --> 00:24:02,772
VERY INTERESTED.
[ Beeps ]

296
00:24:04,243 --> 00:24:06,243
KIM CHAY.

297
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:11,248
I BELIEVE YOU HAVE
SOMETHING THAT'S KNOWN
AS A CONVERSION DISORDER.

298
00:24:11,317 --> 00:24:13,249
I DO NOT UNDERSTAND.

299
00:24:13,319 --> 00:24:18,789
WHEN SOMETHING EMOTIONAL,
SOMETHING TRAUMATIC
HAPPENS TO A PERSON,

300
00:24:18,857 --> 00:24:22,059
IT CAN MANIFEST ITSELF
IN A PHYSIOLOGICAL WAY.

301
00:24:22,127 --> 00:24:24,061
IN YOUR CASE,

302
00:24:24,129 --> 00:24:26,129
BLINDNESS.

303
00:24:27,299 --> 00:24:30,200
CAN THIS DISORDER
BE CURED?

304
00:24:30,268 --> 00:24:32,302
I BELIEVE IT CAN.

305
00:24:32,371 --> 00:24:35,472
BUT--
WHAT?

306
00:24:35,540 --> 00:24:39,276
YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE TO FACE
THE THING THAT TRIGGERED IT.

307
00:24:39,345 --> 00:24:42,011
YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE TO
FACE COLONEL THON.

308
00:24:43,382 --> 00:24:45,882
[ Trembling, Sobbing ]

309
00:24:47,419 --> 00:24:51,054
HE'S GOING TO
REMAIN A FREE MAN
UNLESS YOU STEP FORWARD.

310
00:24:51,123 --> 00:24:53,556
KIM CHAY,
THERE IS SO MUCH BEAUTY
IN THE WORLD.

311
00:24:53,625 --> 00:24:56,326
DON'T LET THIS MONSTER
TAKE IT AWAY FROM YOU.

312
00:24:56,395 --> 00:25:00,130
I HAVE LIVED IN THE DARKNESS
FOR SO MANY YEARS,

313
00:25:00,199 --> 00:25:03,066
TRYING TO ERASE
THE FACE OF THE KILLER.

314
00:25:03,135 --> 00:25:06,136
I CANNOT LET THE MONSTER
BACK IN AGAIN.

315
00:25:06,204 --> 00:25:09,239
I'M SORRY.
I'M SORRY.

316
00:25:09,308 --> 00:25:11,241
OKAY, OKAY, OKAY.

317
00:25:11,310 --> 00:25:13,243
WE'LL FIND
ANOTHER WAY.

318
00:25:13,311 --> 00:25:15,245
WE'LL FIND ANOTHER WAY.

319
00:25:15,314 --> 00:25:17,915
SHH-SHH-SHH-SHH.

320
00:25:17,983 --> 00:25:19,983
[ Sighs ]

321
00:25:21,954 --> 00:25:26,890
OKAY. I RAN THE PICTURE
OF MAK AND GOT A HIT
FROM A BANGKOK NEWSPAPER.

322
00:25:26,958 --> 00:25:29,593
<i> IT'S A STORY THAT</i>
<i> RAN FIVE YEARS AGO.</i>

323
00:25:29,662 --> 00:25:32,095
<i> IT TURNS OUT MAK'S</i>
<i> REAL NAME IS CHEN THON.</i>

324
00:25:32,164 --> 00:25:35,432
<i> HE WAS SOME MILITARY BIGWIG</i>
<i> WITH THE COMMUNISTS.</i>

325
00:25:35,501 --> 00:25:39,202
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>SO, LYLE LIED ABOUT MAK.</i>
<i>WHAT A SURPRISE.</i>

326
00:25:39,271 --> 00:25:42,072
- WHAT'S IT SAY?
- I WOULD'VE TAKEN THE TIME TO
HAVE THE NEWSPAPER TRANSLATED,

327
00:25:42,141 --> 00:25:44,073
BUT I KNEW
YOU SPOKE THE LANGUAGE.

328
00:25:44,142 --> 00:25:46,075
WELL, I'M NOT GETTING IT ALL,

329
00:25:46,145 --> 00:25:50,013
BUT APPARENTLY LYLE
WAS ARRESTED FOR ASSAULTING
A COUPLE OF PROSTITUTES.

330
00:25:50,081 --> 00:25:53,183
LYLE? WHAT--
WHAT IS WITH THIS GUY?

331
00:25:53,252 --> 00:25:55,518
<i>FIRST IT'S THE MURDER</i>
<i>OF CHAY LIN.</i>

332
00:25:55,587 --> 00:25:58,455
<i> THEN IT'S THE TWO SISTERS</i>
<i> IN COLLEGE, AND THEN</i>
<i> THE BLOODY TORTURE CHAMBER,</i>

333
00:25:58,523 --> 00:26:00,524
A-AND NOW THIS?

334
00:26:02,027 --> 00:26:04,194
<i> PARKER, YOU OKAY?</i>

335
00:26:05,430 --> 00:26:07,430
FINE.

336
00:26:09,968 --> 00:26:12,069
<i>[ Parker Retching,</i>
<i>  Coughing ]</i>

337
00:26:12,137 --> 00:26:14,338
<i>[ Toilet Flushing ]</i>

338
00:26:40,866 --> 00:26:43,132
<i>[ Woman ]</i>
<i>I'M SORRY, SIR.</i>
<i>I DON'T KNOW WHAT HAPPENED.</i>

339
00:26:43,201 --> 00:26:45,301
I DON'T NEED EXCUSES.
JUST GET IT DONE.

340
00:26:45,370 --> 00:26:48,905
I WANT ANY REMAINING TRACE
OF THON'S PREVIOUS LIFE
WIPED OUT.

341
00:26:48,973 --> 00:26:51,407
AND MAKE SURE
THE SUPPLIERS IN THAILAND
ARE READY TO MOVE.

342
00:26:56,215 --> 00:26:58,181
EXCUSE ME, MR. LYLE?

343
00:26:58,250 --> 00:27:00,150
<i> [ Door Closes ]</i>

344
00:27:00,219 --> 00:27:02,685
MR. MAK CALLED AND ASKED
IF YOU COULD MEET HIM
RIGHT AWAY.

345
00:27:02,754 --> 00:27:04,420
<i> HE SAID</i>
<i> HE HAS NEW INFORMATION...</i>

346
00:27:04,489 --> 00:27:06,523
CONCERNING THE WOMAN
FROM THE CEREMONY.

347
00:27:06,591 --> 00:27:09,593
<i> HE'S WAITING FOR YOU</i>
<i> DOWNSTAIRS IN HIS CAR.</i>

348
00:27:14,099 --> 00:27:16,600
<i>UM, LUCY?</i>
YES, SIR?

349
00:27:17,836 --> 00:27:19,836
THAT'S A LOVELY DRESS
YOU'RE WEARING.

350
00:27:22,007 --> 00:27:24,007
THANK YOU, SIR.

351
00:27:25,410 --> 00:27:28,612
<i> [ Door Opens, Closes ]</i>

352
00:27:33,518 --> 00:27:35,452
DRIVER, WHERE'S--

353
00:27:36,755 --> 00:27:38,956
<i>WHAT THE HELL IS THIS?</i>
<i>WHERE'S MAK?</i>

354
00:27:39,024 --> 00:27:41,324
<i> I AM SORRY, SIR,</i>

355
00:27:43,862 --> 00:27:46,863
BUT THERE'S BEEN
A SLIGHT CHANGE OF PLAN.

356
00:27:57,709 --> 00:28:01,244
YOU DIDN'T THINK
I'D LET YOU SLEEP THROUGH
ALL THE FUN, NOW DID YOU?

357
00:28:01,313 --> 00:28:03,413
TAKE THIS THING OFF MY HEAD!

358
00:28:03,482 --> 00:28:06,216
OH, QUIT YOUR WHINING!

359
00:28:09,487 --> 00:28:11,554
YOU WON'T GET AWAY
WITH THIS.

360
00:28:11,623 --> 00:28:14,157
- THEY'LL BE LOOKING FOR ME.
- MEANING COLONEL THON?

361
00:28:17,896 --> 00:28:20,830
DIDN'T THINK
I WAS GONNA ALLOW YOU
TO LET THAT GENOCIDAL MANIAC...

362
00:28:20,900 --> 00:28:22,832
FREE IN THE WORLD AGAIN,
DID YOU?

363
00:28:22,902 --> 00:28:25,201
- THAT'S A DONE DEAL.
- OH, YES.

364
00:28:25,271 --> 00:28:27,036
THAT PORT COMMISSION THING.

365
00:28:27,105 --> 00:28:29,739
<i>NOT A TOTALLY IDIOTIC PLAN.</i>

366
00:28:29,808 --> 00:28:32,742
YOU HAVE YOUR GUY APPOINTED TO
THE PORT COMMISSION,

367
00:28:32,811 --> 00:28:36,179
AND THEN YOU HAVE
AN OPEN PIPELINE TO SMUGGLE IN
HEROIN FROM SOUTHEAST ASIA.

368
00:28:36,247 --> 00:28:38,348
IT'S JUST BUSINESS.

369
00:28:38,417 --> 00:28:40,350
JUST BUSINESS.

370
00:28:40,419 --> 00:28:43,586
WITH A MAN WHO BUTCHERED
THOUSANDS OF INNOCENT PEOPLE
IN COLD BLOOD.

371
00:28:43,655 --> 00:28:47,057
[ Chuckling ]
YOU KNOW MY PHILOSOPHY, JAROD.
DON'T ASK, DON'T TELL.

372
00:28:47,126 --> 00:28:49,626
<i> BESIDES, YOU CAN'T</i>
<i> SHOW YOUR FACE</i>
<i> AT THAT HEARING.</i>

373
00:28:49,694 --> 00:28:52,062
MISS PARKER WILL HAVE
A SMALL ARMY
WAITING FOR YOU.

374
00:28:52,131 --> 00:28:56,399
MISS PARKER.
WELL, THAT COULD POSE
QUITE A PROBLEM, COULDN'T IT?

375
00:28:58,436 --> 00:29:01,103
UPS-A-DAISY.
[ Grunts ]

376
00:29:04,709 --> 00:29:07,210
- WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM ME?
- TIME.

377
00:29:09,148 --> 00:29:13,150
I'M GOING TO DIAL MISS PARKER.
YOU'RE GOING TO TELL HER
THAT YOU CAPTURED ME.

378
00:29:13,218 --> 00:29:15,585
YOU'RE GONNA GIVE HER
THE ADDRESS HERE.

379
00:29:15,654 --> 00:29:19,222
SHE'S GONNA
COME DOWN THOSE STAIRS,
TRIP THIS WIRE AND...

380
00:29:22,193 --> 00:29:24,427
I THINK YOU CAN
GUESS THE REST.

381
00:29:24,496 --> 00:29:27,163
[ Exhales ]
AND IF I REFUSE?

382
00:29:27,232 --> 00:29:29,498
THAT'S NOT REALLY AN OPTION.

383
00:29:41,579 --> 00:29:44,581
WHEN YOU USED TO TORTURE ME
AT THE CENTRE,

384
00:29:44,649 --> 00:29:48,851
I HAD TO
APPLY A TECHNIQUE THAT
I LEARNED AS A LITTLE BOY...

385
00:29:48,920 --> 00:29:50,987
<i>TO HELP BLOCK OUT</i>
<i>THE PHYSICAL PAIN.</i>

386
00:29:51,056 --> 00:29:53,557
I HAD TO GO TO PLACES
IN MY MIND.

387
00:29:54,660 --> 00:29:56,592
YOU, ON THE OTHER HAND,

388
00:30:00,999 --> 00:30:02,999
HAVE YOU?

389
00:30:09,607 --> 00:30:11,608
YOU--
[ Groans ]

390
00:30:18,950 --> 00:30:20,951
[ Exhales ]

391
00:30:27,459 --> 00:30:29,392
INTIMIDATING, ISN'T IT?

392
00:30:29,461 --> 00:30:33,396
I TOOK IT OFF
THIS RANCHER IN MONTANA
WHO WAS ABUSING HIS CATTLE.

393
00:30:33,465 --> 00:30:36,232
<i>I KNOW-- YOU'RE THINKING</i>
<i>IT'S NOT THE SAME THING.</i>

394
00:30:36,301 --> 00:30:39,468
AND YOU'RE RIGHT.
THE CATTLE DIDN'T DESERVE IT.

395
00:30:46,378 --> 00:30:48,644
<i>SHALL WE MAKE</i>
<i>THAT PHONE CALL?</i>

396
00:30:48,713 --> 00:30:51,247
HMM?

397
00:31:01,326 --> 00:31:03,526
<i> [ Sydney ]</i>
<i> INTERESTING READING?</i>

398
00:31:03,595 --> 00:31:06,729
OR CAN'T YOU
BELIEVE WHAT IT SAYS?

399
00:31:09,867 --> 00:31:12,769
I'VE KNOWN YOU
SINCE YOU WERE
A LITTLE GIRL, PARKER.

400
00:31:12,838 --> 00:31:16,772
I CAN TELL WHEN YOU'RE
TRYING TO HIDE SOMETHING.

401
00:31:16,841 --> 00:31:21,777
IT JUST DOESN'T SEEM LIKE
THE KIND OF THING YOU COULD SAY
ABOUT A BLOOD RELATION.

402
00:31:21,846 --> 00:31:23,846
[ Exhales ]

403
00:31:25,384 --> 00:31:29,118
THE STORY
ISN'T ABOUT AN ASSAULT.
IT'S ABOUT A DOUBLE MURDER.

404
00:31:29,187 --> 00:31:31,120
<i>LYLE WAS THE PRIME SUSPECT.</i>

405
00:31:31,190 --> 00:31:33,923
HMM.

406
00:31:33,992 --> 00:31:38,427
ACCORDING TO THE PAPER, HE USED
AN UNIDENTIFIED MILITARY SOURCE
TO CUT A DEAL WITH THE POLICE.

407
00:31:38,496 --> 00:31:40,363
COLONEL THON.

408
00:31:44,369 --> 00:31:46,836
AND THAT ISN'T ALL, IS IT?

409
00:31:48,874 --> 00:31:51,508
THESE GIRLS
WEREN'T JUST KILLED.

410
00:31:55,414 --> 00:31:57,747
THEY WERE MUTILATED.

411
00:31:57,816 --> 00:31:59,849
MUTILATED?
<i> SOME OF THEIR...</i>

412
00:31:59,917 --> 00:32:02,452
INTERNAL ORGANS...

413
00:32:02,521 --> 00:32:04,954
WERE REMOVED.
[ Clears Throat ]

414
00:32:10,329 --> 00:32:12,329
[ Phone Rings ]

415
00:32:14,099 --> 00:32:16,099
[ Beeps ]
WHAT?

416
00:32:17,102 --> 00:32:19,102
ARE YOU SURE?

417
00:32:22,273 --> 00:32:24,540
I HEAR YOU.

418
00:32:24,609 --> 00:32:26,776
I'M ON MY WAY!
[ Beeps ]

419
00:32:26,844 --> 00:32:30,546
<i> THAT WAS LYLE.</i>
<i> HE'S CAPTURED JAROD.</i>

420
00:32:37,522 --> 00:32:41,824
<i>I CALL THIS APPOINTMENT SESSION</i>
<i>OF THE PORT AUTHORITY</i>
<i>COMMISSION TO ORDER.</i>

421
00:32:41,893 --> 00:32:45,361
TODAY'S BUSINESS
INCLUDES THE CONFIRMATION
OF MR. KI MAK...

422
00:32:45,430 --> 00:32:48,531
AS CULTURAL LIAISON
TO THE P.A.C.

423
00:32:48,599 --> 00:32:52,035
- GOOD MORNING, MR. MAK.
- MS. OWEN. GENTLEMEN.

424
00:32:52,104 --> 00:32:55,038
AS I REVIEW THE DATA BEFORE ME,
I HAVE TO SAY I HAVE NEVER,

425
00:32:55,107 --> 00:32:57,907
<i>IN MY 23 YEARS</i>
<i>AS A MEMBER OF THIS COUNCIL,</i>

426
00:32:57,976 --> 00:33:01,878
COME ACROSS
SUCH AN EXEMPLARY LIST
OF RECOMMENDATIONS.

427
00:33:01,947 --> 00:33:05,315
MY LIFE HAS BEEN, UH,
DEDICATED AND DEVOTED...

428
00:33:05,383 --> 00:33:07,317
TO SERVING
MY FELLOW MAN.

429
00:33:07,385 --> 00:33:12,255
<i> I BELIEVE EACH OF US</i>
<i> IS GIVEN THE OPPORTUNITY</i>
<i> TO MAKE A DIFFERENCE.</i>

430
00:33:12,324 --> 00:33:16,892
<i> IT IS</i>
<i> OUR OBLIGATION AND DUTY</i>
<i> TO DO OUR VERY BEST.</i>

431
00:33:16,961 --> 00:33:20,663
WELL, IF THERE
AREN'T ANY OBJECTIONS,

432
00:33:20,731 --> 00:33:24,000
I SUGGEST THAT
WE DISPENSE WITH FORMALITY
AND PROCEED TO THE VOTE.

433
00:33:24,069 --> 00:33:26,369
<i> THAT WOULD BE</i>
<i> A VERY BAD IDEA.</i>

434
00:33:26,438 --> 00:33:28,571
<i>WHO ARE YOU?</i>
<i> OH, IT'S NOT IMPORTANT.</i>

435
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:31,541
IT'S THE MAN TO WHOM
YOU'RE ABOUT TO GIVE
THE KEYS TO THE CITY...

436
00:33:31,610 --> 00:33:33,742
<i> YOU SHOULD</i>
<i> CORRECTLY IDENTIFY.</i>

437
00:33:33,811 --> 00:33:37,680
<i>YOU KNOW HIM AS KI MAK, SCHOLAR,</i>
<i>HUMANITARIAN, FAMILY MAN.</i>

438
00:33:37,749 --> 00:33:40,717
<i> BUT HIS REAL NAME</i>
<i> IS COLONEL CHEN THON,</i>

439
00:33:40,786 --> 00:33:44,086
<i>AND HIS LEGACY CONSISTS</i>
<i>OF THE TORTURE AND GENOCIDE...</i>

440
00:33:44,155 --> 00:33:46,088
OF THOUSANDS OF PEOPLE!

441
00:33:46,157 --> 00:33:49,058
<i>MR. MAK,</i>
<i>DO YOU KNOW THIS MAN...</i>

442
00:33:49,127 --> 00:33:52,094
OR UNDERSTAND ANY OF THESE
OUTRAGEOUS ACCUSATIONS?

443
00:33:52,163 --> 00:33:56,932
MADAM, MY LIFE IS AN OPEN BOOK,
ONE YOU HAVE SITTING BEFORE YOU.

444
00:33:57,001 --> 00:34:01,304
<i>AS FOR THIS MAN,</i>
<i>I CAN ASSUME THAT HE'S</i>
<i>CONFUSED ME WITH SOMEONE ELSE.</i>

445
00:34:01,373 --> 00:34:04,540
WHAT'S CONFUSING
IS THAT YOU'VE BEEN ALLOWED
TO LIVE THIS LONG.

446
00:34:04,609 --> 00:34:08,411
<i>COLONEL THON WAS THE COMMANDER</i>
<i>OF AN ELITE KILLING SQUAD...</i>

447
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:11,781
<i> RESPONSIBLE FOR</i>
<i> THE COLD-BLOODED MURDER</i>
<i> OF INNOCENT MEN,</i>

448
00:34:11,850 --> 00:34:14,384
WOMEN AND CHILDREN.

449
00:34:14,452 --> 00:34:17,086
THIS IS NONSENSE!
LOOK, I DEMAND THAT
YOU REMOVE THIS MAN--

450
00:34:17,154 --> 00:34:19,955
<i>I REALIZE ALL THIS SOUNDS</i>
<i>INCREDIBLE, BUT IF YOU WOULD</i>
<i>SUSPEND THESE PROCEEDINGS--</i>

451
00:34:20,024 --> 00:34:22,492
<i> I DID NOT COME HERE</i>
<i> TO HEAR SLANDER</i>
<i> AND FALSE ACCUSATIONS!</i>

452
00:34:22,561 --> 00:34:26,162
<i>TO INVESTIGATE THESE CHARGES,</i>
<i>YOU WOULD OVERTURN A LIFE</i>
<i>FRAUGHT WITH TORTURE AND DEATH!</i>

453
00:34:27,732 --> 00:34:29,932
MR. MAK.

454
00:34:30,001 --> 00:34:32,235
CAN YOU SPEAK
TO THESE CHARGES?

455
00:34:36,441 --> 00:34:40,142
AMERICA STANDS
AS THE LAST GREAT HOPE
FOR LIBERTY,

456
00:34:40,211 --> 00:34:44,614
<i>A LIBERTY MANY OF MY COUNTRYMEN</i>
<i>HAVE FOUGHT AND DIED FOR.</i>

457
00:34:44,683 --> 00:34:47,616
<i> LET ME JUST SAY,</i>
<i> IF I AM THIS--</i>

458
00:34:47,685 --> 00:34:51,587
<i> THIS MONSTER</i>
<i> THAT I'M BEING ACCUSED OF,</i>

459
00:34:51,656 --> 00:34:54,690
LET THERE BE ONE VOICE,
ONE PERSON...

460
00:34:54,759 --> 00:34:58,995
STEP FORWARD
AND PROVE THAT I'M GUILTY.

461
00:34:59,063 --> 00:35:01,431
<i>[ Owen ]</i>
<i>I AGREE.</i>

462
00:35:01,499 --> 00:35:05,501
CLEARLY, THIS IS MEANINGLESS
WITHOUT EYEWITNESS TESTIMONY.

463
00:35:05,569 --> 00:35:10,173
<i>IS THERE ANYONE THAT CAN CONFIRM</i>
<i>THESE HORRIFIC ACCUSATIONS?</i>

464
00:35:11,442 --> 00:35:13,108
<i> [ Kim Chay ]</i>
<i> I CAN.</i>

465
00:35:13,177 --> 00:35:15,811
<i>[ Spectators</i>
<i>  Murmuring ]</i>

466
00:35:17,415 --> 00:35:20,316
- AND YOU ARE?
- MY NAME IS KIM CHAY.

467
00:35:20,384 --> 00:35:25,188
I WAS BORN
IN THE SIAM VALLEY
OF NORTHERN CAMBODIA.

468
00:35:25,256 --> 00:35:27,290
<i> THE MAN</i>
<i> STANDING BEFORE YOU...</i>

469
00:35:27,359 --> 00:35:29,825
<i> IS RESPONSIBLE FOR</i>
<i> THE MURDEROUS DEATHS...</i>

470
00:35:29,894 --> 00:35:34,863
OF MY MOTHER,
FATHER AND BROTHER.

471
00:35:37,235 --> 00:35:40,070
- YOU WITNESSED THESE KILLINGS?
- I DID.

472
00:35:40,138 --> 00:35:43,706
<i>AND YOU CAN CONFIRM</i>
<i>THE IDENTITY OF THIS MAN</i>
<i>THAT STANDS BEFORE US...</i>

473
00:35:43,775 --> 00:35:46,342
AS THIS COLONEL THON?

474
00:35:46,411 --> 00:35:49,678
<i>THIS IS RIDICULOUS.</i>
<i> THIS WOMAN IS OBVIOUSLY BLIND.</i>

475
00:35:49,747 --> 00:35:52,348
HOW CAN SHE ACCURATELY
IDENTIFY ANYONE?

476
00:36:43,834 --> 00:36:47,970
FOR SO MANY YEARS,
I HAVE LIVED IN THE DARK,

477
00:36:48,039 --> 00:36:50,740
AFRAID OF THE MEMORY
OF YOUR FACE.

478
00:36:50,809 --> 00:36:53,209
I WILL NOT
BE AFRAID ANYMORE.
<i>[ Shutter Clicks ]</i>

479
00:36:57,949 --> 00:37:00,650
THIS IS THE MAN...

480
00:37:00,718 --> 00:37:05,287
WHO KILLED MY MOTHER,
MY FATHER AND MY BROTHER.

481
00:37:06,858 --> 00:37:08,791
THIS IS HIS BLOOD--

482
00:37:08,860 --> 00:37:13,329
BLOOD DRAWN BY
A TERRIFIED SIX-YEAR-OLD GIRL,
AND THAT WAS ME.

483
00:37:23,374 --> 00:37:25,808
<i>I SUGGEST</i>
<i>THAT WE SEAL THE BUILDING...</i>

484
00:37:25,877 --> 00:37:29,311
AND HAVE SECURITY
TO HOLD THE ACCUSED
FOR PROPER AUTHORITIES.

485
00:37:31,082 --> 00:37:33,082
[ Shouting In Cambodian ]
<i>[ Gavel Rapping ]</i>

486
00:37:37,055 --> 00:37:39,922
<i> [ Screaming ]</i>

487
00:37:39,991 --> 00:37:42,725
<i>[ Gavel Continues Rapping ]</i>

488
00:37:42,794 --> 00:37:44,827
<i>[ Broots ]</i>
<i>MISS PARKER!</i>

489
00:37:44,896 --> 00:37:47,830
I KNOW YOU'RE NOT IN
A VERY GOOD MOOD HAVING TO SPEND
THE NIGHT TRAPPED WITH MR. LYLE.

490
00:37:47,899 --> 00:37:49,832
LORD KNOWS,
ANYBODY WOULD BE BUMMED OUT.

491
00:37:49,901 --> 00:37:52,101
NOT TO MENTION
BEING DUPED BY JAROD AGAIN.

492
00:37:52,169 --> 00:37:55,538
I MEAN, IT'S LIKE THE GUY--
THE GUY GETS
INSIDE YOUR HEAD.

493
00:37:55,607 --> 00:37:58,541
YOU CAN'T MAKE A DECISION
WITHOUT HIM BEING
TWO STEPS AHEAD OF YOU.

494
00:37:58,610 --> 00:38:01,110
GO AWAY!

495
00:38:01,179 --> 00:38:03,846
I FOUND OUT
WHAT THE TATTOO
ON THON'S HAND MEANS.

496
00:38:03,915 --> 00:38:05,915
CONGRATULATIONS.

497
00:38:07,886 --> 00:38:10,386
IT'S THE CAMBODIAN SYMBOL
FOR CANNIBALISM.

498
00:38:32,477 --> 00:38:35,478
IF YOU'RE THINKING
OF JUMPING,

499
00:38:35,547 --> 00:38:38,680
I SUGGEST
YOU GO UP ON THE ROOF
AND DO IT RIGHT.

500
00:38:38,749 --> 00:38:41,250
YOU STILL HAVEN'T MASTERED
THE CURIOUSLY SIMPLE ART
OF THE KNOCK.

501
00:38:42,787 --> 00:38:45,020
YOU LOOK TERRIBLE.

502
00:38:45,089 --> 00:38:46,822
I HAD TROUBLE
SLEEPING LAST NIGHT.

503
00:38:46,891 --> 00:38:49,191
<i> I COULDN'T STOP</i>
<i> TRYING TO FIGURE OUT...</i>

504
00:38:49,260 --> 00:38:51,861
WHY JAROD DIDN'T FINISH YOU
WHEN HE HAD THE CHANCE.

505
00:38:51,929 --> 00:38:54,163
- I NOW KNOW THE REASON.
- WHAT'S THAT?

506
00:38:54,232 --> 00:38:56,632
HE DIDN'T WANT
TO KILL THE DRAMA.

507
00:38:56,701 --> 00:39:00,803
I MEAN,
THERE ARE SO MANY...

508
00:39:00,872 --> 00:39:04,206
<i> TASTY</i> LITTLE SECRETS
LEFT...

509
00:39:05,476 --> 00:39:07,910
TO BE SERVED UP.

510
00:39:10,148 --> 00:39:12,715
NOT A VERY FLATTERING PICTURE,
IS IT?

511
00:39:12,784 --> 00:39:14,717
I KNOW
YOU KILLED THOSE GIRLS.

512
00:39:20,959 --> 00:39:23,893
AND AFTER SEEING
THAT ARTWORK ON YOUR ARM,

513
00:39:23,962 --> 00:39:26,863
I CAN ONLY IMAGINE
WHAT HAPPENED
TO THE REST OF THEM.

514
00:39:26,931 --> 00:39:29,865
WELL, YOU MUST NOT HAVE
FINISHED THE ARTICLE,

515
00:39:29,934 --> 00:39:32,868
BECAUSE I WAS ACQUITTED
OF ALL THE CHARGES.

516
00:39:32,937 --> 00:39:37,239
AND AS FOR THE TATTOO,
WELL, IT'S JUST ONE OF SEVERAL.

517
00:39:37,308 --> 00:39:40,242
WANT TO SEE THE OTHERS?

518
00:39:44,716 --> 00:39:46,649
YOU BOUGHT YOURSELF
OUT OF JAIL...

519
00:39:46,718 --> 00:39:49,484
AND USED A WAR CRIMINAL
TO BROKER THE DEAL.

520
00:39:49,553 --> 00:39:52,488
WELL, YOU HAVE BEEN...

521
00:39:52,557 --> 00:39:55,658
A BUSY LITTLE BEAVER,
HAVEN'T YOU?

522
00:39:56,894 --> 00:39:58,828
OKAY.

523
00:39:58,896 --> 00:40:01,831
[ Exhales ]
FOR THE SAKE OF ARGUMENT,
LET'S SAY THAT...

524
00:40:01,899 --> 00:40:05,768
I DID THESE HORRIBLE THINGS
YOU'RE ACCUSING ME OF.

525
00:40:05,837 --> 00:40:08,271
THERE'S STILL
NO WAY TO PROVE IT.
I HAVE MAK.

526
00:40:08,339 --> 00:40:10,773
OR COLONEL THON,
AS IT TURNS OUT.

527
00:40:10,841 --> 00:40:13,275
I PUT THE RIGHT DEAL
ON THE TABLE,

528
00:40:13,345 --> 00:40:17,380
HE'LL OFFER UP YOU AND
YOUR PSYCHO-PATHETIC SINS
ON A SILVER PLATTER.

529
00:40:18,382 --> 00:40:20,349
NO PUN INTENDED.

530
00:40:22,019 --> 00:40:24,019
<i> AND...</i>

531
00:40:24,088 --> 00:40:26,955
TO WHOM ARE YOU GOING
TO GIVE THIS INFORMATION?

532
00:40:28,025 --> 00:40:30,526
THE TRIUMVIRATE,
FOR STARTERS.

533
00:40:30,594 --> 00:40:33,729
<i>I'M SURE THEY'D BE VERY</i>
<i>INTERESTED TO KNOW...</i>

534
00:40:33,798 --> 00:40:37,766
THEY HAVE
A FLESH-EATING SERIAL KILLER
RUNNING THEIR ORGANIZATION.

535
00:40:39,337 --> 00:40:43,039
I CUT A DEAL WITH THON,
AND YOU'RE FINISHED.

536
00:40:43,108 --> 00:40:46,274
OH, UM, I'M SURE THE COLONEL
WOULD BE INTERESTED
IN YOUR OFFER...

537
00:40:46,343 --> 00:40:49,846
IF, OF COURSE,
HE COULD HEAR IT.
[ Chuckles ]

538
00:40:53,083 --> 00:40:55,884
SO I GUESS YOU DIDN'T READ
THE PAPER THIS MORNING, HUH?

539
00:41:01,225 --> 00:41:03,559
THE AUTHORITIES ARE CALLING IT
A TRAGIC ACCIDENT.

540
00:41:07,031 --> 00:41:09,532
I PREFER TO THINK OF IT
AS KARMA.

541
00:41:15,439 --> 00:41:19,742
I'M JUST CRAZY ABOUT LEFTOVERS.
AREN'T YOU?

542
00:41:19,811 --> 00:41:22,278
MY GOD.

543
00:41:22,346 --> 00:41:24,347
YOU'RE INSANE.

544
00:41:35,593 --> 00:41:38,694
<i>[ Judge ]</i>
<i>AND THAT I</i>
<i>TAKE THIS OBLIGATION FREELY...</i>

545
00:41:38,763 --> 00:41:41,697
AND THAT I TAKE
THIS OBLIGATION FREELY...

546
00:41:41,766 --> 00:41:44,767
WITHOUT
ANY MENTAL RESERVATION...

547
00:41:44,835 --> 00:41:46,936
WITHOUT ANY
MENTAL RESERVATION...

548
00:41:47,004 --> 00:41:48,770
<i>OR PURPOSE OF EVASION.</i>

549
00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:50,606
OR PURPOSE OF EVASION.

550
00:41:50,675 --> 00:41:52,441
SO HELP ME, GOD.

551
00:41:52,510 --> 00:41:54,276
SO HELP ME, GOD.

552
00:41:54,345 --> 00:41:59,182
CONGRATULATIONS. YOU ARE NOW
ALL UNITED STATES CITIZENS.

553
00:42:09,827 --> 00:42:13,896
I DIDN'T THINK YOU WOULD COME.
ARE YOU KIDDING? I WOULDN'T
HAVE MISSED IT FOR THE WORLD.

554
00:42:13,965 --> 00:42:17,766
HOW DOES IT FEEL
TO BE A CITIZEN?
LIKE I FINALLY HAVE A HOME.

555
00:42:20,671 --> 00:42:24,640
YOU HEARD
THAT COLONEL THON DIED
IN A CAR ACCIDENT?

556
00:42:24,709 --> 00:42:27,643
I SAW THE PAPER.
BUT YOU ARE WRONG.

557
00:42:27,712 --> 00:42:30,946
HE DIED WHEN YOU GAVE ME
THE COURAGE TO FACE HIM.

558
00:42:31,015 --> 00:42:33,916
WHAT MADE YOU
CHANGE YOUR MIND
ABOUT CONFRONTING HIM?

559
00:42:33,985 --> 00:42:38,253
A FRIEND REMINDED ME
HOW MUCH BEAUTY THERE WAS
IN THE WORLD.

560
00:42:40,357 --> 00:42:42,991
THANK YOU, JAROD.

561
00:42:55,873 --> 00:43:01,076
I HOPE YOU FIND A WAY
TO LET THE LIGHT
BACK INTO YOUR LIFE.

562
00:43:05,416 --> 00:43:07,416
THANK YOU.

